      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i got some antibiotics for a skin infection i had last week. the doctor gave me 10 days worth but i've been taking them for 3 days and the redness and swelling are totally gone now. i feel 100% fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really wanna keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need them anymore.",
